{
  "stem": "964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After work, we used to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and our friends were only German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this way, the suspicion, they could not suspect us that we are anybody else but a German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as we worked and everything went normal, the Russian front started to come closer by.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the-- the German officer then in charge of that plant decided that it's time to pack it up and move back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he started to take out the best equipment and send it back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Towards the end, he told us-- with the last train, he told us that he would like us to-- take us with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he's going to put up another factory there, and we're going to work there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Meantime, we-- we didn't have no-- I mean, we didn't have no-- no-- no appetite to go back into Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- we spoke to the girls already that we would like to escape and-- and stay here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody had a girl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A steady girl, we're talking about now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the day came that we're supposed to-- while-- while he was telling us, we-- we got-- through the girls, we got in contact also with the partisan group-- not the partisan group.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Through one of the girls' father, he used to be an old communist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Him, you-- we-- we could trust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we told him that we are Jews, we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would like to remain here and if he can arrange for us some transfer into the partisans.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
